The Book of Knowledge is a good proof of concept, but you're not pleased with how slow it is. Even managing your time efficiently has its limits, you need a better solution.

The Research Completer multiblock machine is exactly what it says on the tin: Feed it power, give it a node to savagely devour with no hint of mercy or remorse like the cold, unfeeling machine that it is, and it will complete research notes for you.

Â§3Don't even bother trying to use this multi without Empowering bees. It'll chew through nodes so quickly you'd spend more time collecting nodes than you would completing research manually. Let stand doing something else while a Book of Knowledge does the research for you.
